          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Veterans and Servicemembers Employment Rights and Housing Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits employment practices that discriminate based on an individual's military service and amends the Fair Housing Act and the Civil Rights Act of 1968 to prohibit housing discrimination against members of the uniformed services.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-12-10T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
